{"tid":2171600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年隆亨邨遭群漢圍斬　殺聲震天","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T05:38:10.000Z","uid":58867,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"98d4d7e36901efd605775024b74765a673b6961e","tid":2171600,"uid":58867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"今日(24日)凌晨接近2時，約8名青年沙田大圍隆亨邨一間中學外籃球場長櫈上聊天，期間被十數名男子追打，部分人更持刀，眾青年逃跑；其中一名年約17歲青年，最終被惡煞擒住圍毆及用刀襲擊，他手腳中刀流血，負傷逃至學心樓對開一個休憩處時不支倒地。<br />\n<br />\n由於正值夜深，現場傳出震天異響，多名街坊被驚醒報案。警方手持盾牌到場時兇徒已四散，並將傷者送院救治，現場血漬斑斑，地面遍布染血紙巾；警員亦檢獲一頂疑屬於傷者的鴨舌帽；在籃球場上亦發現一隻懷疑屬於男傷者右腳穿着的白色球鞋，沙田警區刑事調查隊將案件列傷人，正封鎖現場調查詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_02p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=a81c6c1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地上血漬斑斑。(楊日權攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_03p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=2939093b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n案發現場為沙田大圍隆亨邨學心樓對開休憩處。(楊日權攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_04p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=18213e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地面遍布染血紙巾，以及一頂疑屬於傷者的鴨舌帽。(楊日權攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_05p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=99045b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_06p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=c11af243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在沙田大圍隆亨邨一間中學外的籃球場調查。(楊日權攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200824/photo/bkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_07p.jpg?20200824040628\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200824%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200824023809062-0824_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20200824040628&h=403f9764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員在籃球場上亦發現一隻懷疑屬於男傷者穿着的白色球鞋。(楊日權攝)"},{"pid":"135f5ff831a9f56c1989fbb2ef44473eeb8705db","tid":2171600,"uid":10338,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:17:49.000Z","msg":"警方手持盾牌到場時兇徒已四散<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabb2c1e914cdae660a8d5e5e6f9945dde91d956","tid":2171600,"uid":9564,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f50dc038f9efb9b2eb138627b08da81ae77bdb87","tid":2171600,"uid":39174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"國家幾時先安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"967794d3946104d6c6fa11dee2f4c646a694230d","tid":2171600,"uid":3241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:27:59.000Z","msg":"斬到咁都係用最雞級既刑事調查隊<br />\n噴下反動句子就出重案組<br />\n<br />\n毅進智力果然係與人不同"},{"pid":"29ef3374f783a96475b041bc3091e1a40f907a6d","tid":2171600,"uid":36906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20